    <h1>ThomasNet Industry Podcast Episode 51 features Saman Farid, CEO and Co-Founder of Formic</h1>
    <div class="legal-meta">Thursday, October 13, 2022</div>
  </div>

<figure style="max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px"><img src="/articles/thomasnet-industry-podcast-episode-51-features-saman-farid-ceo-and-co-founder-of-formic/1665684769-podcast-image.png" alt="ThomasNet Industry Podcast Episode 51 features Saman Farid, CEO and Co-Founder of Formic" style="width:100%;height:auto;display:block" /></figure>
  <div class="legal-prose">
<p>The Thomas Industry Podcast is back and better than ever! You don&#x27;t want to miss this episode on automation.</p> <p>&quot;The thing that we&#x27;ve heard over and over and over again from our customers is &#x27;Yeah, we&#x27;ve been planning to automate. We&#x27;re right about to do it. We&#x27;ve been planning this project for the last five or ten years.&#x27; Well, why don&#x27;t I see a robot over here?&quot; asks Saman Farid, CEO of <a href="https://formic.co/?utm_term=formic%20technologies&amp;utm_campaign=GS+-+Brand&amp;utm_source=adwords&amp;utm_medium=ppc&amp;hsa_acc=9687645776&amp;hsa_cam=16094157250&amp;hsa_grp=132511993349&amp;hsa_ad=600318012854&amp;hsa_src=g&amp;hsa_tgt=kwd-1265467052127&amp;hsa_kw=formic%20technologies&amp;hsa_mt=e&amp;hsa_net=adwords&amp;hsa_ver=3&amp;gclid=Cj0KCQjwy5maBhDdARIsAMxrkw2xkuZQlSmjy0jC1svFul2S6gsshcP0fi8BDuJ0Vkan6rhWU-80mjwaArOXEALw_wcB">Formic</a>. Host Cathy Ma chats with Farid about why automation is no longer a luxury for manufacturers and how Formic&#x27;s Robots-as-a-Service (RaaS) business model is making automation more accessible.</p> <p>The podcast can be found on the <a href="https://go.skimresources.com/?id=193416X1670854&amp;isjs=1&amp;jv=15.3.0-stackpath&amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thomasnet.com%2Finsights%2Fthomas-industry-update-podcast%2F&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fpodcasts.apple.com%2Fus%2Fpodcast%2Fputting-off-automating-you-can-now-use-robots-by-the-hour%2Fid1484079735%3Fi%3D1000582430808&amp;xs=1&amp;xtz=240&amp;xuuid=fbf332e06a86b7e6414cea479e55b27d&amp;xjsf=other_click__auxclick%20%5B2%5D">Apple podcast</a> app, <a href="https://open.spotify.com/episode/4ecOaFEKRN24X5XmhSSG47">Spotify</a>, and <a href="https://www.stitcher.com/show/thomas-industry-update-podcast/episode/putting-off-automating-you-can-now-hire-robots-by-the-hour-207542549">Stitcher</a>.</p>
